{"title":"STL","uid":"48433a70b7e09e957d48f01fa1012852","slug":"STL","date":"2023-01-19T07:56:32.557Z","updated":"2023-01-19T08:00:30.991Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/STL.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"STL\"><a href=\"#STL\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"STL\"></a>STL</h1><p><strong>STL是什么：STL是标准模板库的意思，是一个c++的模板库，其内置了不少可以直接拿来用的函数模板和容器</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"STL容器\"><a href=\"#STL容器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"STL容器\"></a>STL容器</h2><h3 id=\"vector\"><a href=\"#vector\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"vector\"></a>vector</h3><h4 id=\"头文件\"><a href=\"#头文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"头文件\"></a>头文件</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include&lt;vector&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"定义一个vector数组\"><a href=\"#定义一个vector数组\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义一个vector数组\"></a>定义一个vector数组</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">vector&lt;type&gt; v;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"操作\"><a href=\"#操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作\"></a>操作</h4><p><em><strong>时间复杂度：O(1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>向数组最后插入新的元素x</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">v.push_back(x);</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>向数组最后删除一个元素x</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">v.pop_back(x);</code></pre>\n\n<p><em><strong>时间复杂度O(n)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>获取数组长度</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">v.size()</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>清空数组</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">v.clear()</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>返回开头元素的指针</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">v.begin()</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>返回指向末尾元素的下一个指针</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">v.end()</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>返回最后一个元素</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">v.back();</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"set-amp-multiset\"><a href=\"#set-amp-multiset\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"set&amp;multiset\"></a>set&amp;multiset</h3><h4 id=\"特点\"><a href=\"#特点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"特点\"></a>特点</h4><p><strong>自己会从小到大排好序，set去重而multiset不去重</strong></p>\n<h4 id=\"头文件-1\"><a href=\"#头文件-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"头文件\"></a>头文件</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include&lt;set&gt;\n#include&lt;multiset&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"定义一个set-x2F-multiset\"><a href=\"#定义一个set-x2F-multiset\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义一个set&#x2F;multiset\"></a>定义一个set&#x2F;multiset</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">set &lt;type&gt; s;\nmultiset &lt;type&gt; s;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"操作-1\"><a href=\"#操作-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作\"></a>操作</h4><p><em><strong>时间复杂度O(log n)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>插入新元素x</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">s.insert(x)</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>删除元素x</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">s.erase(x)</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>查询元素x是否存在（若不存在则返回s.end( )）</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">s.find(x)</code></pre>\n\n<p><em><strong>时间复杂度O(n)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>清空集合</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">s.clear()</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>返回指向开头元素的指针</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">s.begin()</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>返回指向末尾的下一个元素的指针</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">s.end()</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"如何用auto遍历一个set\"><a href=\"#如何用auto遍历一个set\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"如何用auto遍历一个set\"></a>如何用auto遍历一个set</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include&lt;multiset&gt;\nusing namespace std;\nmultiset&lt;int&gt; s[N];\nfor(auto i:s[tmp])\n    cout&lt;&lt;i&lt;&lt;&#39; &#39;;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"map-amp-unordered-map\"><a href=\"#map-amp-unordered-map\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"map&amp;unordered_map\"></a>map&amp;unordered_map</h3><h4 id=\"特点-1\"><a href=\"#特点-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"特点\"></a>特点</h4><p><strong>由{键，值}对组成的集合，以某种比较键大小关系的谓词进行排序（map和unordered_map排序方式不同，具体怎么应该？不用管？）</strong></p>\n<h4 id=\"头文件-2\"><a href=\"#头文件-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"头文件\"></a>头文件</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include&lt;map&gt;\n#include&lt;unordered_map&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"定义一个map-x2F-unordered-map\"><a href=\"#定义一个map-x2F-unordered-map\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义一个map&#x2F;unordered_map\"></a>定义一个map&#x2F;unordered_map</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">map&lt;type1,type2&gt; mp1;\nunordered_map&lt;type1,type2&gt; mp2;\n&#x2F;&#x2F;type1类似数组下标的类型\n&#x2F;&#x2F;type2类似数组存的值的类型</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"操作-2\"><a href=\"#操作-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作\"></a>操作</h4><p><em><strong>时间复杂度在map上是O(log n)而在unordered_map上是O(1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>查找一个键值对</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">mp[1]&#x3D;2;</code></pre>\n\n<p><em><strong>时间复杂度O(n)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>清空映射关系</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">mp.clear();</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"stack\"><a href=\"#stack\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"stack\"></a>stack</h3><h4 id=\"头文件-3\"><a href=\"#头文件-3\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"头文件\"></a>头文件</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include&lt;stack&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"定义一个stack\"><a href=\"#定义一个stack\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义一个stack\"></a>定义一个stack</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">stack&lt;type&gt; st;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"操作-3\"><a href=\"#操作-3\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作\"></a>操作</h4><p><strong>向栈顶压入新元素x</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">st.push(x);</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>出栈一个元素（注意没有返回值）</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">st.pop();</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>查询栈顶的元素</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">st.top();</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>查询栈是否为空</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">st.empty();</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"queue\"><a href=\"#queue\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"queue\"></a>queue</h3><h4 id=\"头文件-4\"><a href=\"#头文件-4\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"头文件\"></a>头文件</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include&lt;queue&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"定义一个queue\"><a href=\"#定义一个queue\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义一个queue\"></a>定义一个queue</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">queue&lt;type&gt; q;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"操作-4\"><a href=\"#操作-4\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作\"></a>操作</h4><p><strong>返回队头元素</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">q.front();</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>返回队尾元素</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">q.back();</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>向队尾压入x</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">q.push(x);</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>弹出队头元素</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">q.pop();</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>判断队列是否为空</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">q.empty();</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"priority-queue\"><a href=\"#priority-queue\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"priority_queue\"></a>priority_queue</h3><h4 id=\"特点-2\"><a href=\"#特点-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"特点\"></a>特点</h4><p><strong>优先队列是一个类似于set的东西（实际是一个堆），默认队列头部的元素优先级最高。因为它是一个队列，所以只能访问第一个元素</strong></p>\n<h4 id=\"头文件-5\"><a href=\"#头文件-5\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"头文件\"></a>头文件</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include&lt;priority_queue&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"定义一个优先队列\"><a href=\"#定义一个优先队列\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义一个优先队列\"></a>定义一个优先队列</h4><p><strong>默认从大到小排序</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">priority_queue&lt;type&gt; q;</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>从小到大排序</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">priority_queue&lt;int,vector&lt;int&gt;,greater&lt;int&gt;&gt;q;</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><em><strong>三个参数</strong></em></p>\n<ol>\n<li>存放元素的类型</li>\n<li>用什么存放（默认vector）</li>\n<li>按什么操作函数排序（默认less）</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>注意这里的less和greater都在头文件 <functional> 中</strong></p></blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"操作-5\"><a href=\"#操作-5\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作\"></a>操作</h4><p><strong>查询队头元素</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">q.top();</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>向队列中加入一个元素x</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">q.push(x);</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>弹出队头元素</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">q.pop();</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>查询队列是否为空</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">q.empty();</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"STL函数\"><a href=\"#STL函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"STL函数\"></a>STL函数</h2><h3 id=\"sort\"><a href=\"#sort\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"sort\"></a>sort</h3><h3 id=\"next-permutation\"><a href=\"#next-permutation\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"next_permutation\"></a>next_permutation</h3><h4 id=\"什么是全排列\"><a href=\"#什么是全排列\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"什么是全排列\"></a>什么是全排列</h4><p><strong>一个全排列是指$a_1$到$a_n$的值都属于[1,n]，且x在[1,n]中，x有且仅出现一次</strong></p>\n<h4 id=\"具体用法\"><a href=\"#具体用法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"具体用法\"></a>具体用法</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">void solve()&#123;\n\tint a[4]&#x3D;&#123;1,2,3,4&#125;;\n    sort(a,a+4);\n    do&#123;\n        for(int i&#x3D;0;i&lt;4;i++)\n            cout&lt;&lt;a[i]&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;;\n        cout&lt;&lt;endl;\n    &#125;while(next_permutation(a,a+4));\n&#125;\n&#x2F;&#x2F;我们可以发现next_permutation是按字典序一个个遍历其全排列的种数，即如果我一开始的序列定为4 3 2 1的话，它最后输出的也仅仅是4 3 2 1，然后就跳出循环了</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"lower-bound-amp-upper-bound\"><a href=\"#lower-bound-amp-upper-bound\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"lower_bound()&amp;upper_bound()\"></a>lower_bound()&amp;upper_bound()</h3><h4 id=\"lower-bound\"><a href=\"#lower-bound\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"lower_bound\"></a>lower_bound</h4><h5 id=\"函数原型\"><a href=\"#函数原型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"函数原型\"></a>函数原型</h5><p><strong>原型1</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">template &lt;class ForwardIterator, class T&gt;\nForwardIterator lower_bound (ForwardIterator first, ForwardIterator last,  const T&amp; val);</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>原型2</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">template &lt;class ForwardIterator, class T, class Compare&gt;\nForwardIterator lower_bound (ForwardIterator first, ForwardIterator last, const T&amp; val, Compare comp);</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>模板参数解释</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>ForwardIterator就是一个迭代器，vector&lt; int &gt; v，v数组的首元素就是 v.begin()</li>\n<li>T&amp;val , 就是一个T类型的变量</li>\n<li>Compare 就是一个比较器，可以传仿函数对象，也可以传函数指针</li>\n</ol></blockquote>\n<h5 id=\"函数作用\"><a href=\"#函数作用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"函数作用\"></a>函数作用</h5><p>​\t前提是有序的情况下，lower_bound返回指向第一个值不小于val的位置，也就是返回第一个大于等于val值的位置。（通过二分查找）</p>\n<h5 id=\"参数、返回值含义\"><a href=\"#参数、返回值含义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参数、返回值含义\"></a>参数、返回值含义</h5><p><strong>first,last</strong>: 迭代器在排序序列的起始位置和终止位置，使用的范围是[first,last).包括first到last位置中的所有元素<br><strong>val</strong>: 在[first,last)下，也就是区分（找到大于等于val值的位置，返回其迭代器）<br><strong>comp</strong>： 主要针对于原型二，传一个函数对象，或者函数指针，按照它的方式来比较<br><strong>返回值</strong>：返回一个迭代器，指向第一个大于等于val的位置</p>\n<h5 id=\"例子\"><a href=\"#例子\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"例子\"></a>例子</h5><p><em><strong>原型一 例子</strong></em></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;\n#include &lt;algorithm&gt;\n#include &lt;vector&gt;\nusing namespace std;\n\nint main()\n&#123;\n\tvector&lt;int&gt; v&#x3D; &#123;3,4,1,2,8&#125;;\n\t&#x2F;&#x2F;先排序\n\tsort(v.begin(),v.end()); &#x2F;&#x2F; 1 2 3 4 8\n\t\n\t&#x2F;&#x2F; 定义两个迭代器变量 \n\tvector&lt;int&gt;::iterator iter1;\n\tvector&lt;int&gt;::iterator iter2; \n\t\n\titer1 &#x3D; lower_bound(v.begin(),v.end(),3);&#x2F;&#x2F;迭代器指向3\n\titer2 &#x3D; lower_bound(v.begin(),v.end(),7);&#x2F;&#x2F;迭代器指向8（因为第一个大于等于8）\n\t\n\tcout &lt;&lt; iter1 - v.begin() &lt;&lt; endl; &#x2F;&#x2F;下标 2\n\tcout &lt;&lt; iter2 - v.begin() &lt;&lt; endl; &#x2F;&#x2F;下标 4 \n\tsystem(&quot;pause&quot;);\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>总结</strong>：需要注意的是如果例子中（val &gt;&#x3D; 8）,那么迭代器就会指向last位置，也就是数组尾元素的下一个，不管val多大，迭代器永远指向尾元素的下一个位置</p>\n<p><em><strong>原型二 例1</strong></em></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;\n#include &lt;algorithm&gt;\n#include &lt;vector&gt;\nusing namespace std;\n\n\nint main()\n&#123;\n\tvector&lt;int&gt; v &#x3D; &#123; 3, 4, 1, 2, 8 &#125;;\n\t&#x2F;&#x2F; 无序数组，不用sort排序，下面调用lower_bound排序\n\n\t&#x2F;&#x2F; 定义两个迭代器变量 \n\tvector&lt;int&gt;::iterator iter1;\n\tvector&lt;int&gt;::iterator iter2;\n\n\t&#x2F;&#x2F;less&lt;int&gt;() 是建小堆，排升序。\n\t&#x2F;&#x2F;所以数组 v &#x3D; &#123;1,2,3,4,8&#125; \n\t&#x2F;&#x2F;我们找第一个大于等于1的，那肯定就是首元素1了\n\t&#x2F;&#x2F;我们找第一个大于等于8的，没有，所以就指向数组最后一个元素8了\n\titer1 &#x3D; lower_bound(v.begin(), v.end(), 1, less&lt;int&gt;());&#x2F;&#x2F;\n\titer2 &#x3D; lower_bound(v.begin(), v.end(), 8, less&lt;int&gt;());&#x2F;&#x2F;\n\n\tcout &lt;&lt; iter1 - v.begin() &lt;&lt; endl; &#x2F;&#x2F;下标 所以就是 0\n\tcout &lt;&lt; iter2 - v.begin() &lt;&lt; endl; &#x2F;&#x2F;下标 所以就是 4\n\tsystem(&quot;pause&quot;);\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>总结</strong>：我们原型2的第四个参数（比较器）可以用来排序，再来获取大于等于val值的迭代器</p>\n<p><em><strong>原型二 例2 仿函数传参</strong></em></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">typedef struct Student\n&#123;\n\tint _id;  &#x2F;&#x2F;学号\n\tint _num; &#x2F;&#x2F;排名\n\n\tStudent(int id, int num)\n\t\t:_id(id)\n\t\t, _num(num)\n\t&#123;&#125;\n\t\n&#125;Stu;\n\nstruct CompareV\n&#123;\n\tbool operator() (const Stu&amp; s1,  const Stu&amp; s2)&#x2F;&#x2F;  排名升序\n\t&#123;\t\n\t\treturn s1._num &lt; s2._num;\n\t&#125;\n&#125;;\n\nint main()\n&#123;\n\tvector&lt;Stu&gt; vS &#x3D; &#123; &#123; 101, 34 &#125;, &#123; 103, 39 &#125;, &#123; 102, 35 &#125; &#125;;\n\n\n\t&#x2F;&#x2F;CompareV()排完序后是这个丫子\n\t&#x2F;&#x2F;101 34\n\t&#x2F;&#x2F;102 35\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;103 39\n\tauto iter &#x3D; lower_bound(vS.begin(), vS.end(), Stu(200,33), CompareV());\n\tcout &lt;&lt; iter - vS.begin() &lt;&lt; endl; &#x2F;&#x2F;我们就找到了按仿函数排序(找排名比33大的位置 就是0）\n\tsystem(&quot;pause&quot;);\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"upper-bound\"><a href=\"#upper-bound\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"upper_bound\"></a>upper_bound</h4><p>​\t用法和上面类似。<strong>只是把lower_bound的大于等于换成大于</strong>。仿函数等等<strong>全是相同的用法</strong></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"STLSTL是什么：STL是标准模板库的意思，是一个c++的模板库，其内置了不少可以直接拿来用的函数模板和容器 STL容器vector头文件#include&lt;vector&gt; 定义一个vector数组vector&lt;type&gt; v; 操作时间复杂度：O(1) ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"5.6k","symbolsTime":"5 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#STL\"><span class=\"toc-text\">STL</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#STL%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">STL容器</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#vector\"><span class=\"toc-text\">vector</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A4%B4%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">头文件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAvector%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84\"><span class=\"toc-text\">定义一个vector数组</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">操作</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#set-amp-multiset\"><span class=\"toc-text\">set&amp;multiset</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">特点</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A4%B4%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">头文件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAset-x2F-multiset\"><span class=\"toc-text\">定义一个set&#x2F;multiset</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">操作</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%94%A8auto%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAset\"><span class=\"toc-text\">如何用auto遍历一个set</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#map-amp-unordered-map\"><span class=\"toc-text\">map&amp;unordered_map</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">特点</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A4%B4%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">头文件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAmap-x2F-unordered-map\"><span class=\"toc-text\">定义一个map&#x2F;unordered_map</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C-2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">操作</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#stack\"><span class=\"toc-text\">stack</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A4%B4%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">头文件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAstack\"><span class=\"toc-text\">定义一个stack</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C-3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">操作</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#queue\"><span class=\"toc-text\">queue</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A4%B4%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">头文件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAqueue\"><span class=\"toc-text\">定义一个queue</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C-4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">操作</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#priority-queue\"><span class=\"toc-text\">priority_queue</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9-2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">特点</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A4%B4%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">头文件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%BC%98%E5%85%88%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">定义一个优先队列</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C-5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">操作</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#STL%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">STL函数</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#sort\"><span class=\"toc-text\">sort</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#next-permutation\"><span class=\"toc-text\">next_permutation</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF%E5%85%A8%E6%8E%92%E5%88%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">什么是全排列</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">具体用法</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#lower-bound-amp-upper-bound\"><span class=\"toc-text\">lower_bound()&amp;upper_bound()</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#lower-bound\"><span class=\"toc-text\">lower_bound</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%8E%9F%E5%9E%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">函数原型</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">函数作用</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E3%80%81%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E5%80%BC%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">参数、返回值含义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BE%8B%E5%AD%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">例子</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#upper-bound\"><span class=\"toc-text\">upper_bound</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Aurora","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"决策树","uid":"c8a7e9308e269c0b57685bf049081ac1","slug":"决策树","date":"2023-01-18T08:36:07.944Z","updated":"2023-01-18T08:38:23.710Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/决策树.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"决策树1.定义 为达到目标而进行一定选择的过程就是决策树，在机器学习中常被用于分类 2.决策树的组成 节点：节点会根据样本的特征做出判断 根节点：最初的分支点 子结点 叶子节点 边：指示着方向 3.决策树的衡量标准：熵 热力学：用于描述一个系统内部的混乱程度 决策树：用于描述分支...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.6k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"Aurora","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true}}